Class Exam

java.lang.Object
comp3111.examsystem.tools.Entity
comp3111.examsystem.entity.Exam
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Entity>
public class Exam extends Entity
Represents an exam in the examination system. This class encapsulates details about the exam, including its name, associated course, duration, publish status, and related question keys.
